Class Account

java.lang.Object
Account
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Account>
public class Account extends Object implements Comparable<Account>
Account class represents a bank account with basic functionalities such as deposit, withdrawal, balance updates, and account management. It implements the Comparable interface to allow comparison of accounts based on account numbers. Author: George Seriani
